%%{ init: { 'theme': 'dark' } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant ORAC as ORAC :8133
    participant PV2 as Pane-Vortex :8132

    Note over CC,PV2: PreToolUse Flow
    CC->>ORAC: POST /hooks/pre-tool-use
    ORAC->>ORAC: m14 middleware: assign RequestId, start tracing span
    ORAC->>PV2: GET /field/state
    PV2-->>ORAC: {order_parameter, k_effective, phases}
    ORAC->>ORAC: m11 pre_tool: inject field context, routing decision
    ORAC->>ORAC: m18 breaker: check circuit state
    ORAC->>ORAC: m35 tokens: check budget
    ORAC-->>CC: 200 {allow: true, headers: {field_context}}

    Note over CC,PV2: PostToolUse Flow
    CC->>ORAC: POST /hooks/post-tool-use
    ORAC->>ORAC: m12 post_tool: extract tool outcome
    ORAC->>PV2: POST /sphere/{id}/tool-use
    PV2-->>ORAC: 200 {hebbian_updated: true}
    ORAC->>PV2: POST /sphere/{id}/status
    PV2-->>ORAC: 200 {status: "working"}
    ORAC->>ORAC: m15 hebbian: local weight update
    ORAC->>ORAC: m18 breaker: update failure count
    ORAC-->>CC: 200 {processed: true}

    Note over CC,PV2: Quality Gate
    ORAC->>PV2: GET /field/state
    PV2-->>ORAC: {order_parameter: 0.997}
    ORAC->>ORAC: m21 decision: evaluate r_trend
    alt r below threshold
        ORAC->>PV2: POST /conductor/action
        PV2-->>ORAC: 200 {action: "reduce_k"}
    end
